title: Hero Therapy
description:
A short story from the Dr. Alpha universe. The hero Nightwatch has been going through a hard time and decided to try therapy. Unfortunately, she gets roped into talking about a tough event in her life when her therapist notices her injuries.

This my first attempt to making short story motion comics. So, feel free to let me know what you think and thank you for watching!
